'''Domain Jamaane''' was an influential [[Domain]] among the [[Yuuzhan Vong]]. What made Domain Jamaane unique was that it was one of the few Domains which was not confined to a single caste of Yuuzhan Vong society. They had proficient [[Shaper caste|Shapers]] and [[Priest caste|Priests]], and numerous [[Warrior caste|Warriors]]. The clan produced an above-average number of [[Supreme Commander (Yuuzhan Vong rank)|Supreme Commanders]], and also three [[Warmaster]]s. But the most famous member of the family was an [[Intendant caste|Intendant]] by birth: [[Shimrra Jamaane]]. Shimrra was a candidate for [[Supreme Overlord]], and he strongly disagreed with Supreme Overlord [[Quoreal]]'s decision about not invading [[The galaxy/Legends|the galaxy]]. Domain Jamaane was not considered aggressive, but the opportunity for invasion was too great. Gathering other loyal domains, Domain Jamaane launched the [[Jamaane coup]], which overthrew Quoreal and installed Shimrra as the [[Supreme Overlord]] of the [[Yuuzhan Vong]].

